    "Additionally, the lack of blockchain interoperability standards makes it difficult to integrate different blockchain networks and medical devices.Researchers have proposed various security mechanisms for ensuring medical data security in IoT-based bio-and medical informatics, including secure communication protocols, access control mechanisms, encryption, and secure storage.",
    "They have also developed secure data aggregation mechanisms allowing medical data aggregation from multiple sources while preserving data privacy and confidentiality [150].",
    "To address the lack of transparency and explainability of AI algorithms, researchers have proposed the use of explainable AI algorithms and AI interpretability techniques that identify factors that contribute to the decision-making process.",
